subsection.def:
customer
                    (客戶) means any person having an account or
                other dealing, transaction or arrangement with MEFIL;

existing
                    (現有) means existing, outstanding or in force
                immediately before the appointed day;

liabilities
                    (債務) includes duties and obligations of every
                description (whether present or future, actual or contingent);

MEFIL
                    (中東財務) means Middle East Finance
                International Limited;
